verbose_text: The purpose of our analysis was to explore the relationship between pain and fatigue with daily activity and work productivity, in patients from a randomized, double-blind, phase 3 clinical trial of baricitinib, an oral, selective inhibitor of Janus kinase (JAK) 1 and JAK2 [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: inhibitor of Janus kinase (JAK)1 and JAK2
